description: In issue #5, horror movie antics and dinner party excitement abound! What will happen during the DOUBLE DATE OF DOOM?
name: Book Five

volume.name: Bonnie N. Collide, Nine to Five

description: Haruto feels horrible when Oto got beaten up. If only he had come to a decision sooner, he could have been the one to save her. Not only did his archrival Tenma Hase of Momonozono Academy rescue Oto from her bullies, he also made a hefty donation in Oto's name to let her stay at Eitoku! What should Haruto do now?
name: Chapter 13

description: DEADTOOTH is a horror/werewolf comic book.

Plunged into an environment of foreign people, strange food, and round-the-clock hard work, Sister Long struggles to stay positive about her role as a missionary. However, she finds things to love about her new home in Japan and tries to connect with the people.
name: Month 4: May

volume.name: DENDO: One Year and One Half in Tokyo

description:
Battle 02

Dae is up for his second match, but his new opponent is more than he can handle. And the referee has no intention of making things easy on him.
name: Battle 2

description: What holds more secrets - the heart of a woman in love or the deepest, darkest level of Dreamland? The answers may shock you!

Chapter 4

The townspeople of Morton rise up against the Nazi invaders, but all Jo can concentrate on is saving her daughter.
name: Chapter Four

description: Flutter, Volume Two takes place six months after Volume One leaves off as Lily learns that even a 15 year-old shape-shifter can't run away from her problems. With her loved ones in danger, she returns to St. Charles to hide her real identity and live as a boy. But knowing what she's capable of, can Lily be content as a popular high school varsity quarterback?
name: Don't Let Me Die Nervous

description:
Thunderbird

As the Genocide Project closes in, Jacob tries to save his new friends from their wrath...while they try to save Jacob from himself.
name: Chapter 3 - Thunderbird

description:
Olga the Owl

After finding an egg in the forest, a fox suddenly becomes a single dad, trying his best to raise a baby owl named Olga whom he has decided to adopt. How will little Olga learn what it means to be an owl when her dad is a fox? And what will the fox do when one day Olga decides she herself wants to become a fox, too?

Olga the Owl is a heartwarming short story for kids and grown-ups alike.
name: Olga the Owl

description: The second chapter of The Happiness Agent picks up where chapter one left off, with Lorelai on the run, and on the hunt for whoever or whatever it is that is after her. But will her memory hacking give her the answers she wants, or dig her deeper into the trouble she's found herself in?
name: Chapter Two

description: William, Helen and Rex have discovered Darlon's intentions to conquer both worlds. Time is precious and help is far away.

volume.name: The Hidden Treasure & The Witch's World

description:
Holy Cow Comics featuring The Lavender Dot

Don't do the crime if you can't stand the rhyme! Join The Lavender Dot in an Iambic Pentameter inspired free-for-all against the vile and violent Scarface McStripe! It's "poetic justice" at its best! Also, stumble through the misadventures of The Awful Lawfuls, Mysterious Guy, The Scarlet Grackle, Doc Sinews, Cap'n Zero and Mr. Scurvy and their foredoomed struggles with Evil Floyd Clemmens and his subhuman Bad Dads! Mindless mayhem as you like it!
name: The Lavender Dot

description: With one last thing weighing on his mind, is it even worth it to finish this final goal?! Meeting new people along the way helps, but will it benefit him or hinder him in the long run?
The charming, bizarre, and true story of CYNTHIA, the world's most famous mannequin -- and her creator, fashion pioneer LESTER GABA.

The noise of thunder, part two.

Is there somewhere safe for Tessa to hide from Saturn and his army? With her memory partially restored, but still powerless, the top priority for our red-haired, curvaceous heroine is to find allies!
name: The Noise of Thunder, Part Two

description: Barely surviving the blast and ensuing assault- Toran, Mili, Duncan, and Kaiya make their way into the surrounding Wastes. In the distance they can see the source of the carnage- a column of pure blue light. Deciding to investigate the source of the shadows they make their way there- and lose Toran along the way.

Mad Dog prt.3

Having learned the identity of the werewolf that attacked him, Shawn finds himself caught between conflicting accounts of why two former friends are now sworn enemies. After hearing both sides of the story Shawn is left with a choice: believe the tragic story of a broken man, or stand by his new vampire friend accused of a horrible betrayal.

BONUS STORY: The Life and Times of Gary the Tentacle Monster. This is the story of Gary, just a guy with wants to fall in love and have a family. He also happens to be a tentacle beast.
name: Mad Dog prt.3

description:
'M.W.F. Main Event' Part 3

It's 1973 and the wrestling territory in Florida has never looked so misfit!..

After getting a glimpse of seeing the Bald-Headed Freak causing some havoc at the Universal House of Pancakes, back at the Sportsplex, the first M.W.F. match is underway!... David Crass takes on Matt Maverick in pro wrestling's first eye-removal match... and you can bet Mad Mike is prepared to suspend the disbelief!
name: M.W.F. Main Event Part 3

description:
Taming the rats

Is this a dagger I see before me? No, tis the 16th issue of New Stuff! Join Trudy and Corky for another award winning performance. That is, if Beryl and Stan don't ruin it for them.
name: Taming the Rats

description:
Redridge Express

Next Town Over's sixth chapter, wherein separate designs on a train and its freight unite Black and Hunter on the railways.
name: Redridge Express

description:
Staring at the World Through My Rearview Part Two

Adam, John, and Leslie were just normal kids gearing up for winter vacation when a poorly officiated government leads us to nuclear holocaust. All of humanity is lost in one day, except for 3. Swept away on a flying saucer, they escape annihilation only to find themselves 67 years in the past in ROSWELL, NEW MEXICO!
name: Staring at the World Through My Rearview Part Two

description:
Chapter 2

Lanius murders the old man, and tries to get away with it, with tragic results. Meanwhile Dupin questions Annabell Lee about her mysterious encounter with Ligeia.
name: Chapter 2

description:
You're Ruining My High!!

Unfazed by their awkward first date, Eden invites Eric and Dice over to her house for dinner. Relieved that he has a second chance, Eric accepts and gladly brings Dice along (in a glass cup). Eric's learned from his mistakes and is ready to make this date a success... Will this night have a better ending?
name: You're Ruining My High!!

description:
Gullyfluff

A gunslinger guides a family across the American West in search of new hope. On a journey filled with danger at every turn, the group must look within to face their greatest enemy. With greed and fear overshadowing them all, the wisdom of a single gunslinger stands as the last hope for the honorable.
name: Gullyfluff

description:
a second helping

Scoundrel's Quest is set in a fantasy world. In which our scoundrel's "procure" certain items and/or riches for others or themselves. During which they erm... have a lot of adventures. 65 pages
name: A Second Helping

description:
Shorts + Losses Vol. 3

A seasoned pilot leads his team back from a successful mission during World War I, only to run into the greatest enemy ace ever -- the Red Baron, a young immigrant comes to America in search of a better life for his family and learns how to bottle success and create a fortune, an enemy sniper pins down an Army patrol until in Baghdad -- welcome to the third collection of Shorts + Losses.

Starpunch Girl, a cosmic entity with the power of stars in her fists, creates a race of human beings to battle the Black Hole Bandits that enslaved her home world. The Black Hole Bandits are led by her nemesis since galactic grade school, Blackhole Boy.

Starpunch Girl - Chapter Two, Part 2:

While traveling via space-limousine to meet her creations, Starpunch Girl has a nightmare about her tragic past.
name: God Becomes Warlord Part 2

description: Unexpected danger looming over the entire city marks a new chapter in the adventures of our heroes.

The Trail team finally decrypt one of Marco Polo's letters and locate one of the artefacts that he had left behind, with their adversaries hot on their heels. Meanwhile, Allie and Kai seem to have shaken theirs and are making progress with Columbus' book offering a new lead in the quest to reveal the age-old secret of the Biblical Three Kings.
Wart continues his dangerous journey across dimensions. But now he is not alone anymore! Help comes for several sides.
In issue 2, Jo has to deal with some stuff. Will she oversleep? Will things smooth out with Renee? Will there still be a cat? More characters! More locations! More emotions!

volume.name: Where Do We Go From Here?

description:
Desperate Gambit

As Ambassador Benton Hawkes travels to Mars on a critical diplomatic mission, unknown forces launch a third attempt on his life. Space pirates, a new breed of military astronauts-for-hire, have boarded his ship, the Man O' War. Now Hawkes, his allies, and a contingent of Marines, led by Sgt. Wagner, hold off his assailants in a struggle that claims lives on both sides - and reveals the ambassador's surprising new ally: Dina Martel.
name: Desperate Gambit

description:
The prequel to Zero Hunters is here in a four issue mini-series titled Zero Hunters: Dravald! See how Dravald became a vampire and his first battle with Garrick (named Tristan Macready in his first life) back in a time long ago.

This issue - Dravald is transformed into a vampire for the first time. No one is safe within the castle.

It's a battle as old as Betty VS Veronica -- Archie, the clumsiest teen in Riverdale versus Mr. Lodge, the man with the most expensive breakable things! The redheaded disaster finds a way to cause Old Man Lodge a headache every time he visits. Unfortunately for him, his daughter loves Archie! What's a billionaire to do? Read this jumbo-sized digital exclusive and find out!
The monks welcome Nova to Reba monastery.

Bayani, a boy of 11, is desperately trying to care for his sick father (a fisherman) and keep food on the table for his small family. Unfortunately, the sun has been shining down on the islands for the last month and night refuses to fall. The land is growing parched from the constant heat and the fish are moving further and further away from shore. During this disaster, the rain god, Pati', recruits Bayani to undertake a quest rescuing the nine kidnapped daughters of Lady Moon from the horrible monsters of lore. Bayani embarks on a great adventure with his friend, Tala, and using their wits, the kids defeat one hideous creature after another in their quest to rescue each of the Moon's daughters and ultimately save their village.
name: And the Old Ghosts

description:
Unto the Undreaming Eye - Part 1

Facing the dangers of Kadath, Captain Anna and her crew sail to a dark harbor seeking forbidden knowledge that promises a way home. But the Captain has plans of her own, plans that may spell doom for her men.
name: Unto the Undreaming Eye - Part 1

volume.name: Dark Anna and the Pirates of Kadath

description:
The World That Doesn't Exist

Our main character, Deadwood, is tasked with locating and retrieving a high profile cancer researcher named Edwin Grae. His search leads him to the headquarters of the private security firm Blitzkrieg. This is where our story begins to unfold.
name: The World That Doesn't Exist

description: Sabbaticals picks up after the events of Monsterology 101, with several team members pursuing their own agendas. The Lamont Institute may have stumbled, but it takes more than death to stop their plans, and now they are aware of Samwi's potential, she has become their quarry. Professor Tovar's parasitic secret is leading him into the deep darkness, towards a fate that may have consequences far beyond ridding himself of his personal burden.

What lurks behind your greatest nightmares? Only the Spook King knows. He's on a violent quest to harness the evil from some of the most evil dreams from 7 of the most sinful dreamers the world has known. Part one of this horrifying anthology features the talents of Raphael Moran, Erik Craddock, Logan Faerber, Francesco Iaquinta, Marc Borstel and many others.
name: Gluttony and Envy

description: Daniel's mom should be happy he's finally making friends. It's too bad they may be the ghosts of children who died in their new home. Isabel would give her life to protect her son and she may just have to.

THE GATEKEEPER FILES is an adventure series narrated by Anansi, the chief record-keeper and librarian of the Gatekeepers. They are a group of semi-mortal guardians who seek to help defend the sovereignty of 101 dimensional realms. They live in a sort of dimensional nexus known as The Hall of Doors, from where they watch and record all significant disruptions of ten-thousand worlds.

Like the Gatekeepers, the idea of the series is to unite indy comic book writers and artists who are tired of the corporate machine stealing their work for pennies and forcing them to create stories they do not themselves enjoy.

Each creator gets to tell their own stories, with their own characters, whom they own and control completely. The collective benefits in networking, cross-collaboration, cross-marketing and camaraderie is very exciting. In addition, all contributors and readers are free to sell copies of the book at $10 profit per unit sold, benefiting both the creators and readers.
name: TPB

description:
Awakening

The city of Junessa has been in quarantine for the past ten years, trapped alone with thousands of monsters and no help coming. Only the rich and their staff have survived through safety in numbers. Hope has possibly arrived in the form of a mysterious man who seems to have found the chosen one who could end the horror. Unfortunately, she has no interest in being a hero and may prove to be the villain.
name: Awakening

description:
Life

We meet Sy Jones in the aftermath of his mother's death. Seemingly orphaned, he goes forward depressed; a shadow of the child he once was. Without his mentor to guide him, who might he become with no one to look up to? In this time, he comes to school on a Saturday to serve a given detention. Within this brief window he unknowingly comes to face his own death and chooses to see it through and end the sadness. However is this the true end, or the start of his life, after a death.
name: Episode 1 - Life

description:
A young woman named Cass just moved into a decrepid old house with her fiancé, Chang. They got the house for cheap and asked no questions.

But there is something inside the house with them. Something terrible.

Strange handprints on the wall and whistling in the night are just the beginning.

Can Richard Karnak's wonderful death science save the day?

A Rough Guide To Lap-Land

Lap-land USA: When another dancer becomes the victim of the mysterious SCAREFACE, and the LLPD deny they have a serial attacker on their hands, sex-criminologist KINKI AGGRO and her decidedly un-trusty sidekick MUGGINS take matters into their own hands, encountering Pole-Dancers, Bible-Bashers, Sleazy Clubs, Super-Freaks and Girl-Bands along the way!
name: Turning Ugle Part 1 of 3: A Rough Guide To Lap-Land

description:
Kouki's twin older brother, Keiki, has decided to work as a part-time waiter during one of the most important summer of their lives! Worried about his sibling's college career, Kouki decides to take matters into his own hands. But when he goes to the cafe, Kouki realizes the manager is GAY?! What does this mean for him and his brother? Will Kouki be able to get out of this dilemma, or will things only get worse? Also, see what happens when the Internet-famous "Kazushi" finally decides to face his real life terrors...

Contents

  • Some Like It Hot!
  • Some Like It Hot! #2
  • Equatorial Coefficient
  • Love Connect www.love_connect
name: Vol. 1

description:
Lynx: Call me G-d!

Enjoy sci-fi, martial arts, action and adventure? Lynx begins with an otherworldly being materializing above earth, and being confronted by hostile and super-powered earthlings. Who are both sides? Find out by reading!
name: Lynx: Call me G-d!

description: Moon in the Trees is a comic anthology, a selection of five short stories written by Ronald Montgomery and illustrated by a bevy of amazing artists, including James Giar, Tim Switalski, Wendell Cavalcanti, and Lars Kramhoft. This poignant collection sends you on a multi-genre story experience, delivering tales of the true nature of man's best friend in the heat of battle, the vagaries of real life paralleled in cinema, and zombie infestations of the middle ages and 20th Century war.

Aritz and his companions travel to Mexico to take part in a reackets competition. They lend their assistance to a boy who takes them on a journey to the lands of the Huichol indians. Here, our heroes will discover an unknown world in which nothing is quite what it appears to be.

Smile for the Camera

A cat burglary launches a journalist into the seedy underbelly of Hollywood and a reclusive starlet with a penchant for murder. An anorexic supermodel struggles to survive a celebrity cult and its new pretty face, her pop star, ex-lover. The last independent photo journalist lands in Hong Kong to cover US military action against media pirates.
name: Smile for the Camera

description:
Four centuries ago, Tink, celestial defender of humanity, and Utnapishtim, the oldest living human, devised a plan to save Earth from inter-dimensional encroachment.

Today, six powerful teenagers are unknowingly bringing that plan to fruition.
name: The Great Game: Volume 2 Chapter 1

description: Zombies! Spies! The Wild West! On assignment to investigate an undead outbreak in the Pacific Northwest of 1877, Agent Wade becomes the quarry in a grueling marathon chase; and in Chicago, Agent Flynn confronts dangerous anti-evolution protestors. Then, the agents race to stop the infection that's turning residents of a religious colony red-skinned, ravenous, and possessed, according to the familiar-looking Father von Becker who has seized control.
name: Volume Two

description:
Celebrating S.H.I.E.L.D.’s 50th anniversary, Marvel proudly presents the very first S.H.I.E.L.D. adventures! In 1965, having revolutionized everything from super heroes to war and Westerns, Stan Lee and Jack Kirby set their sights on the spy game. Cold War covert ops had been dominating headlines, so they created an international organization to protect the Marvel Universe. Headed by Nick Fury, and featuring Tony Stark and the Howling Commandos, S.H.I.E.L.D. boasted amazing gadgets, world-dominating villains and the debut of the awesome Helicarrier! These inaugural adventures include the first appearances of Hydra and A.I.M.; a team-up with Captain America; and countless threats to every man, woman and child on planet Earth. Get ready to dive into the world of the Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.!

Collects Strange Tales (1951) #135-150, Fantastic Four (1961) #21, Tales of Suspense (1959) #78.
name: TPB

volume.name: S.H.I.E.L.D. by Lee & Kirby: The Complete Collection

description: Same day Return is a slice of life comic from Sean Azzopardi.

Orientation: chapter one

Follow Cherri Creeper as she discovers that there is indeed a School to teach fledgling Vampires to Drink Responsibly!
name: Orientation Chapter 1

description: Welcome to the future where the last vestige of mankind now resides on the Moon. David Bell only wants to know one thing: What happened to Earth? With the help of his best friend and a daring young woman from the nomadic Duster people, they will journey across the moon and beyond facing myth, monsters and more to find answers and save mankind's future.
name: Vol. 1

description: Skull fights the war on drugs in an unusual way.
name: Skull

description: Swamp Punks is a future-tech, dystopian swamp world adventure book.
name: Chapter One

description:
Disowned but not disloyal, Alexandria Castlehawk Metterson is the captain of the guard in a city abandoned to attacking forces - a city she once ruled as a Duke's heir. Now under the iron fist of the Raikshor, Alexandria and her group try to keep the peace while revolution rumbles through the alleys of Castleforge.

But when peace comes at too high a price, how far will she go to keep it?

Young scientist Justin Sharp is contracted by the U.S. Military to crack the secrets of time travel. Before he hands the project over to the military, he just needs to make one small adjustment to his past...and that's when things get crazy.

Immortality

Omar Mirza and Khurram Mehtabdin bring you the next installment the Zindan series, Issue #1: Immortality. Readers are thrown into a world of madness by new lead penciller Mike Krome. Mayhem reigns throughout Mughal India as Zain and Timur quest to recapture Zindan's worst criminals. The de facto leaders of the fugitives, Wayl al-Athab known as the Immortal, leads the escapees on a chaotic rampage with the help of magic, mysticism and other worldly forces. Follow Zain and Timur as they seek to combat the evil as The Last Ansaars of Zindan.
name: Immortality

description: A photographer, Evlyn Wescott, became blind after an accident in his studio that cost his wife her life. Several years after that tragic event, Wescott is now the victim of a string of attempts against his own life which he fortuitously eludes, managing to have a narrow escape. When a model he worked with before gets killed, the photographer starts thinking that the murder might be linked to one of his old pictures, and asks Julia to shed some light on the situation...
name: L'immagine Perduta

description: Paris, 1790. The revoutionary wind is blowing away the "Ancient Regime", but the end of the old privileges means the beginning of a new political intrigue: the season of Terror is almost here. Charles-Henri Sanson, the “executioner of the King” who conscientiously served Louis XVI, is now the "executioner of the people" and he's ready to cut the king's head. His obscure vicissitudes go on in the shadow of the guillotine… A story of love and death, power and justice, loneliness and revenge!
name: Il Boia Di Parigi
